The '''2016 Pan American Road Cycling Championships''' took place at [[San Cristóbal, Táchira]], [[Venezuela]], May 19–22, 2016.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ansur.am/venezuela-cic/venezuela-acoge-campeonato-panamericano-de-ciclismo-de-ruta_n37058 |title=Venezuela acoge campeonato panamericano de ciclismo de ruta |location=Tachira, Venezuela |agency=PL |newspaper=ANSUR |language=Spanish |date=19 May 2016 |accessdate=21 May 2016}}</ref>
==Medal summary==
