'''Hamilton Parish Football Club''' are a Bermudan football club based in [[Hamilton Parish, Bermuda]]. They currently play in the [[Bermudian Premier Division]].

==History==
Also named ''Hamilton Parish Hot Peppers'',<ref>[http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160111/SPORT01/160119968 Thompson sets sights on topping goal charts] - Royal Gazette</ref> the club have been in the [[Bermudian Premier Division]] since winning promotion in March 2013.<ref>[http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20130325/SPORT01/703259972 Parish,St David's clinch promotion] - Royal Gazette</ref><ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesb/berm2013.html#first Bermuda 2012/13] - RSSSF</ref> They secured the First Division title a week after promotion was confirmed.<ref>[http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20130401/SPORT01/704019985 Hamilton Parish clinch First Division league title] - Royal Gazette</ref>

